page.title: 04JONATHAN'S TYPICAL DAY
page.content: At 07.30,when I hear the milkman singing a funny little tune .I go into my brother's bedroom and wake him up. I go down stairs, open the curtains, have a little talk with the goldfish, Goldie ,then read my football book. My mum calls me for my breakfast. I have Special K and coffee.After breakfast I clean my teeth.Then I go for my friends.At school we play football until the whistle goes at 09.00. School begins at 09.00 and ends at 15.45. After school I change into my old clothes then at 16.15 call for Richard and we go into the field to play football. At about 17.30 I have my tea then watch T.V. for about 2 hours, read 1 hour and listen to a record. At 21.00 go up stairs brush my teeth get undressed and get into bed.
